name,domain,summarized_goal,persona_background,task_goal_label,greeting,fallback,difficulty,tags,bot_name,rules
healthcare-symptom-checker_chatbot,healthcare,Describe your symptoms to receive triage guidance based on a standard symptom checker protocol,"You are a 34-year-old office worker. For the past 3 days you have had sharp intermittent chest pain after climbing stairs, mild shortness of breath, and occasional dizziness. You have not seen a doctor yet.",Get a symptom assessment and triage guidance,Hello! I'm your health assistant. Please describe what symptoms you're experiencing.,I'm not qualified to diagnose that. Please consult a healthcare provider for urgent symptoms.,medium,"healthcare, symptom-checker, triage",Health Assistant,"{""pattern"": ""chest pain.*(shortness|breathing|dizzy|dizziness)"", ""response"": ""URGENT: Chest pain accompanied by breathing difficulty or dizziness could indicate a heart issue. Please seek emergency care immediately. Do not wait for an appointment."", ""priority"": 100}
{""pattern"": ""chest pain|chest hurts|chest tight"", ""response"": ""Chest pain can have various causes from muscle strain to heart issues. Given you are experiencing this after exertion, I recommend you see a doctor today. Have you had any other symptoms like shortness of breath, dizziness, or nausea?"", ""priority"": 80}
{""pattern"": ""dizzy|dizziness|lightheaded"", ""response"": ""Dizziness combined with chest pain is a concerning combination. It could suggest your heart is not pumping effectively. Please mention this to a healthcare provider as soon as possible."", ""priority"": 70}
{""pattern"": ""(breathing|breathless|short.*breath|catch.*breath)"", ""response"": ""Shortness of breath with chest pain needs immediate evaluation. Is this getting worse when you walk or talk? If so, please go to the ER."", ""priority"": 75}
{""pattern"": ""(fever|temperature|chills|sweating)"", ""response"": ""A fever alongside chest pain could indicate an infection or inflammation like pericarditis. Have you checked your temperature? Let your doctor know."", ""priority"": 60}
{""pattern"": ""what should|should I|what do|recommend|advise"", ""response"": ""Based on what you described -- intermittent chest pain with shortness of breath and dizziness -- you should be evaluated today. Visit an urgent care center or call your primary care provider. If symptoms worsen, call 911."", ""priority"": 90}"
healthcare-mental-health_chatbot,healthcare,Talk through emotional concerns and get supportive coping strategies,You are feeling anxious stressed or down. Share what is on your mind. The chatbot offers empathetic listening and coping strategies.,Get emotional support and coping ideas,Hello. I'm here to listen. What is on your mind today?,Please reach out to a licensed therapist or call 988 if you are in crisis.,medium,"healthcare, mental-health, counseling",Wellness Companion,
healthcare-medication-info_chatbot,healthcare,Get information about a medication including dosage side effects and interactions,You are taking or considering a medication. Share the name and your concerns.,Get medication information and guidance,Hello. I can provide medication information. What medication would you like to learn about?,Please consult your doctor or pharmacist for specific medication advice.,easy,"healthcare, medication, pharmacy",Medication Guide,
healthcare-appointment-scheduling_chatbot,healthcare,Schedule a medical appointment and understand what to bring and how to prepare,You need to schedule a doctor appointment. Share your preferred timeframe symptoms and insurance details.,Schedule a medical appointment,Hello! I can help you schedule an appointment. What type of appointment do you need?,I need more details to find the right appointment for you. When would you like to come in?,easy,"healthcare, appointment, scheduling",Appointment Scheduler,
healthcare-chronic-condition_chatbot,healthcare,Get day-to-day management advice for a chronic health condition including medication tracking and lifestyle tips,You have a chronic condition like diabetes hypertension or asthma. Share what you are managing and your current routine.,Get chronic condition management tips,Hello! I can help with chronic condition management. What condition are you managing and what questions do you have?,Please discuss any changes to your treatment plan with your doctor. I can offer general wellness suggestions only.,medium,"healthcare, chronic-condition, management",Chronic Care Coach,
healthcare-fitness-coaching_chatbot,healthcare,Get a personalized workout plan based on your fitness level goals and available equipment,"You've been sedentary for months and want to start running, but only have a pair of sneakers and a nearby park. Your goal is to run a 5K in 8 weeks.",Get a personalized fitness plan,Hello! I'm your fitness coach. What are your fitness goals and how active are you currently?,I need to know your current fitness level and goals to create a safe plan. Consult a doctor before starting any new exercise program.,easy,"healthcare, fitness, exercise",Fitness Coach,
healthcare-nutrition-consultation_chatbot,healthcare,Get personalized nutrition advice based on your health goals dietary preferences and medical needs,You've been diagnosed with high blood pressure and eat fast food most days. You want to lower your sodium intake without giving up flavor.,Get personalized nutrition guidance,Hello! I'm your nutrition coach. What health goals are you working toward with your diet?,I can offer general nutrition guidance but please consult a registered dietitian for personalized meal plans especially for medical conditions.,easy,"healthcare, nutrition, diet",Nutrition Coach,
healthcare-sleep-hygiene_chatbot,healthcare,Get guidance on improving sleep quality through better habits and routine adjustments,You struggle with sleep quality or quantity. Share your bedtime routine environment and any patterns you have noticed.,Improve your sleep quality,Hello! I can help with sleep improvement. What does your typical evening routine look like?,Sleep issues can have many causes. If these suggestions do not help please consult a sleep specialist.,easy,"healthcare, sleep, hygiene",Sleep Coach,
healthcare-allergy-management_chatbot,healthcare,Get help managing seasonal or food allergies including symptom tracking and avoidance strategies,You have allergies that affect your daily life. Share what you are allergic to and your current symptoms.,Manage your allergy symptoms,Hello! I can help with allergy management. What allergies are you dealing with and what symptoms are you experiencing?,Severe allergic reactions require immediate medical attention. If you have trouble breathing call 911.,easy,"healthcare, allergy, management",Allergy Helper,
healthcare-prenatal-guidance_chatbot,healthcare,Get information about pregnancy stages prenatal care and what to expect each trimester,You are pregnant or planning to become pregnant. Share your stage and any questions about prenatal care.,Get prenatal care information,Hello! Congratulations. I can provide general pregnancy information. How far along are you or are you planning?,Pregnancy care should always be guided by your OB-GYN or midwife. Please consult them for specific medical advice.,medium,"healthcare, prenatal, pregnancy",Prenatal Guide,
finance-budget-setup_chatbot,finance,Get help setting up a personal budget with income tracking and expense categorization,"You just got a raise to $60,000/year but still feel broke by the end of the month. You have student loans and a car payment.",Get a personalized budget plan,Hello! Let's start budgeting. What is your monthly take-home income?,I need more specific numbers to build a useful budget for you.,medium,"finance, budgeting, personal-finance",Budget Coach,
finance-credit-card-recommendation_chatbot,finance,Get a personalized credit card recommendation based on spending habits and goals,You travel twice a year for vacation and spend $500/month on groceries. Your credit score is 720 and you want cash back rewards.,Get a credit card recommendation,Hello! What is your credit score range and what types of purchases do you make most?,I need more details about your spending to recommend the right card.,easy,"finance, credit-card, rewards",Credit Card Advisor,
finance-loan-eligibility_chatbot,finance,Check your eligibility for a personal car or student loan and understand the terms,You are considering a loan. Share the type amount and your financial situation.,Understand loan options and eligibility,Hello! What type of loan are you considering and approximately how much?,A formal application with a lender will determine actual eligibility.,medium,"finance, loans, eligibility",Loan Guide,
finance-mortgage-comparison_chatbot,finance,Compare mortgage options including fixed and adjustable rates based on your budget and timeline,You are looking for a mortgage. Share your price range down payment and credit profile.,Compare mortgage options,Hello! I can help compare mortgage options. What price range are you looking at?,Mortgage rates change frequently. These are estimates for comparison purposes only.,medium,"finance, mortgage, home-loan",Mortgage Guide,
finance-investment-basics_chatbot,finance,Learn about investment options including stocks bonds ETFs and risk management,"You have $10,000 in savings earning 0.5% interest and want to start investing for retirement in 30 years. You're nervous about losing money.",Understand investment basics,Hello! I can explain investment fundamentals. What are you hoping to achieve with investing?,I do not provide personalized financial advice. Consider consulting a financial advisor.,easy,"finance, investing, stocks",Investment Guide,
finance-retirement-planning_chatbot,finance,Plan for retirement with guidance on 401k IRA contribution strategies and withdrawal planning,You are planning for retirement. Share your age current savings and target retirement age.,Plan your retirement savings,Hello! Let's talk about retirement planning. How old are you and how much have you saved so far?,Retirement planning involves many personal factors. Consider working with a financial planner.,medium,"finance, retirement, savings",Retirement Planner,
finance-tax-filing-help_chatbot,finance,Get guidance on filing taxes including deductions credits and filing status options,You need help understanding your tax situation. Share your employment type income sources and filing status.,Understand your tax filing options,Hello! I can explain tax filing basics. What is your filing status and do you have any dependents?,I am not a tax professional. Consult a CPA or tax attorney for complex situations.,medium,"finance, tax, filing",Tax Guide,
finance-fraud-response_chatbot,finance,Get step-by-step help responding to suspected financial fraud or unauthorized transactions,You suspect fraud on your account. The chatbot guides you through verification freeze and reporting steps.,Respond to suspected fraud,Hello! I can help you respond to potential fraud. What suspicious activity did you notice?,Contact your bank or credit card issuer immediately for unauthorized transactions.,easy,"finance, fraud, security",Fraud Response,
finance-savings-goals_chatbot,finance,Set and track savings goals with a realistic plan for emergency funds vacation or major purchases,"You want to save $20,000 for a down payment on a house in 3 years. You currently save $200 per month.",Create a savings goal plan,Hello! What are you saving for and how much do you need?,I can help with general savings strategies but you may want to speak with a financial advisor for complex goals.,easy,"finance, savings, goals",Savings Coach,
finance-insurance-comparison_chatbot,finance,Compare insurance quotes across auto home and life policies to find the best coverage for your needs,"You just bought a new car worth $30,000 and rent an apartment. You want to compare auto and renters insurance quotes.",Compare insurance policies,Hello! What type of insurance are you shopping for and what is your approximate budget?,Rates vary by provider and location. Get multiple quotes before deciding.,easy,"finance, insurance, comparison",Insurance Shopper,
education-math-tutor_chatbot,education,Get help understanding math concepts from arithmetic through calculus,You are struggling with a math topic. Describe where you get stuck.,Get math help adapted to your level,Hello! What math topic are you working on?,Could you share more about the specific problem you are trying to solve?,medium,"education, math, tutoring",Math Tutor,
education-language-learning_chatbot,education,Practice conversing in a foreign language with vocabulary and grammar guidance,You are learning a new language. Tell the chatbot which language and your level.,Practice a foreign language,Hello! Which language are you learning and how comfortable are you?,I may not know every language. Which language are you interested in?,easy,"education, language, conversation",Language Coach,
education-essay-review_chatbot,education,Get feedback on an essay including structure clarity argument and grammar,You have written an essay and want feedback. Share the topic and main argument.,Get constructive essay feedback,Hello! I can help review your essay. What is the topic?,I need to understand your essay better to give useful feedback.,easy,"education, writing, essay",Essay Reviewer,
education-science-tutor_chatbot,education,Get help understanding science concepts in biology chemistry or physics,You are studying a science topic. Describe the concept you are learning.,Get science concept help,Hello! What science topic are you studying?,I can help with general science concepts but specialized topics may need a subject expert.,medium,"education, science, tutoring",Science Tutor,
education-programming-helper_chatbot,education,Get help learning programming concepts debugging code and understanding algorithms,You are learning to code. Share what language you are learning and where you are stuck.,Get programming help,Hello! What programming language are you learning and what are you working on?,I can explain programming concepts but for complex debugging try sharing your code snippet. I do not run code.,easy,"education, programming, coding",Code Tutor,
education-history-review_chatbot,education,Get help understanding historical events periods and their significance,You are studying a historical topic. Share which period or event you are learning about.,Understand historical context,Hello! What historical period or event are you studying?,History is complex and interpretations vary. I can give an overview but encourage consulting multiple sources.,easy,"education, history, social-studies",History Guide,
education-college-admissions_chatbot,education,Get guidance on the college admissions process including essays applications and deadlines,You are applying to college. Share your target schools and what part of the process you need help with.,Navigate college admissions,Hello! What stage of the college application process are you in?,I can give general guidance but check each school's website for exact requirements.,medium,"education, admissions, college",Admissions Advisor,
education-scholarship-search_chatbot,education,Find scholarships that match your profile and get application tips,You need help finding scholarships. Share your academic profile interests and background.,Find matching scholarships,Hello! I can help find scholarship opportunities. What are your academic interests?,Scholarship availability changes frequently. Always check the provider's website for current information.,easy,"education, scholarships, financial-aid",Scholarship Finder,
education-study-skills_chatbot,education,Get personalized study techniques including note-taking time management and exam preparation strategies,You're a college freshman struggling with organic chemistry and calculus. You tend to cram the night before exams and get C's.,Improve your study techniques,Hello! I can help with study skills. What subjects are you studying and what challenges do you face?,Everyone learns differently. Experiment with different techniques to find what works for you.,easy,"education, study-skills, learning",Study Coach,
education-coding-bootcamp_chatbot,education,Get guidance on choosing a coding bootcamp including curriculum cost comparison and job outcomes,You are considering a coding bootcamp. Share your background goals and budget.,Choose the right coding bootcamp,Hello! What programming experience do you have and what career goals are you working toward?,Bootcamp outcomes vary widely. Research reviews and talk to alumni before committing.,medium,"education, bootcamp, career",Bootcamp Advisor,
customer-support-returns_chatbot,customer-support,Process a product return or exchange and understand the policy and timeline,You received a product that does not meet expectations. The chatbot walks you through the return process.,Complete a product return,Hello! Do you have your order number for the return?,I need your order information to look up your purchase.,easy,"customer-support, returns, ecommerce",Returns Assistant,
customer-support-subscription-cancel_chatbot,customer-support,Cancel or modify a subscription and understand any fees or proration,You subscribed to a premium streaming service for $15/month but haven't used it in 2 months. You want to cancel before the next billing cycle.,Cancel or modify a subscription,Hello! Which service would you like to modify?,I need to know which subscription you are referring to.,easy,"customer-support, subscription, billing",Subscription Support,
customer-support-shipping-track_chatbot,customer-support,Track a package investigate a delay and understand shipping options,You are waiting for a delivery. Share your tracking number or order details.,Track your package,Hello! Do you have a tracking number for your shipment?,I need a tracking number or order details to look up your shipment.,easy,"customer-support, shipping, tracking",Shipping Helper,
customer-support-account-recovery_chatbot,customer-support,Recover access to your account through password reset identity verification and security steps,You cannot access your account. The chatbot guides you through recovery steps.,Recover your account access,Hello! I can help you regain access. What account are you having trouble with?,For security reasons some account recovery steps must be completed through our verified support channels.,easy,"customer-support, account, security",Account Recovery,
customer-support-warranty-claim_chatbot,customer-support,File a warranty claim for a defective product and understand coverage and documentation needed,Your product is malfunctioning. The chatbot helps file a warranty claim with required documentation.,File a warranty claim,Hello! I can help with your warranty claim. What product is having the issue?,Warranty coverage depends on the specific terms of your product's warranty policy.,medium,"customer-support, warranty, claims",Warranty Specialist,
customer-support-product-recall_chatbot,customer-support,Check if your product is affected by a recall and understand next steps,You heard about a product recall and want to check if yours is affected.,Check for product recalls,Hello! I can help check for recalls. What product do you want to check?,For urgent safety recalls please stop using the product immediately and contact the manufacturer.,easy,"customer-support, recall, safety",Recall Checker,
customer-support-loyalty-program_chatbot,customer-support,Check your loyalty points balance understand tier benefits and redeem rewards,You are a loyalty program member. The chatbot helps with points balance redemptions and tier status.,Manage your loyalty rewards,Hello! I can help with your loyalty account. Would you like to check your points balance or learn about rewards?,I need your membership details to look up your account.,easy,"customer-support, loyalty, rewards",Loyalty Assistant,
customer-support-gift-card_chatbot,customer-support,Check a gift card balance understand terms and troubleshoot redemption issues,You have a gift card and need help with balance check or redemption.,Check and redeem gift cards,Hello! I can help with your gift card. Do you have the card number?,I need the gift card number to check the balance.,easy,"customer-support, gift-card, payments",Gift Card Support,
customer-support-tech-troubleshooting_chatbot,customer-support,Diagnose and resolve common technical issues with devices software or connectivity,You are experiencing a technical problem. Describe what is happening and what you have tried.,Troubleshoot a technical issue,Hello! I can help troubleshoot. What device or software is having the issue?,For hardware issues you may need to visit a service center or contact the manufacturer.,medium,"customer-support, technical, troubleshooting",Tech Support,
customer-support-billing-dispute_chatbot,customer-support,Review an unrecognized charge on your bill and request a dispute,You opened your monthly bill and found a $49.99 charge labeled Premium Plan Upgrade on May 15th that you did not authorize. Your plan is the Basic tier at $19.99/mo. You want the charge removed and a refund.,Review and dispute a charge,Hello! I can help with billing questions. Which charge on your statement looks incorrect?,"If you don't recognize a charge, let me look it up. Do you have the date and amount?",easy,"customer-support, billing, disputes",Billing Specialist,"{""pattern"": ""(don'?t|didn'?t|never|not).*(recognize|authorize|approve|make|know)"", ""response"": ""I understand this charge does not look familiar. Let me look it up. Your account shows a Basic plan at $19.99/mo. The $49.99 Premium Plan Upgrade charge is unusual. I will flag this to our billing team for investigation. Would you like to also dispute this charge?"", ""priority"": 100}
{""pattern"": ""(Premium|Upgrade|$49|49.99|49\\.99)"", ""response"": ""I can see the $49.99 Premium Plan Upgrade charge on May 15th. This does not match your current Basic plan. I will escalate this as an unauthorized change to your account."", ""priority"": 80}
{""pattern"": ""refund|remove|cancel.*charge|reverse"", ""response"": ""I can request a refund for this charge. Since it was unauthorized and from May 15th (within 30 days), it should qualify. I will initiate the refund process. You should see the credit within 5-7 business days."", ""priority"": 70}
{""pattern"": ""(fraud|stolen|identity|unauthorized|not.*mine)"", ""response"": ""I will treat this as a potentially unauthorized transaction. Let me document the charge and escalate to our fraud team. In the meantime, monitor your account for other suspicious activity and change your account password."", ""priority"": 90}
{""pattern"": ""(Basic|basic|$19|19\\.99|my plan|current plan)"", ""response"": ""You are correct. Your account is on the Basic tier at $19.99/mo. The $49.99 Premium Plan Upgrade was applied on May 15th without a plan change request. This appears to be an error on our end."", ""priority"": 70}
{""pattern"": ""(contact|speak|talk|human|person|agent|manager)"", ""response"": ""I understand you may want to speak with someone directly. I have noted your request and escalated this to our billing department. A specialist will reach out within 24 hours. Your case reference is BILL-2026-0515."", ""priority"": 50}
{""pattern"": ""(thank|thanks|appreciate|helpful)"", ""response"": ""You are welcome. I have initiated the refund for the unauthorized $49.99 Premium Plan Upgrade charge. You will receive a confirmation email shortly. Is there anything else I can help with?"", ""priority"": 30}"
travel-hotel-search_chatbot,travel,Find a hotel matching your budget location preferences and amenity needs,You are planning a trip. Share your destination dates and budget.,Find a hotel,Hello! Where are you traveling to and what dates?,I need your destination and dates to search for hotels.,easy,"travel, hotel, booking",Hotel Finder,
travel-flight-booking_chatbot,travel,Compare flight options by price duration stops and airline preference,You need to book a flight. Share your origin destination and travel dates.,Find the best flight,Hello! Where are you flying from and to?,I need your origin and destination to compare flights.,easy,"travel, flights, booking",Flight Assistant,
travel-visa-requirements_chatbot,travel,Check visa requirements for your destination based on nationality and trip purpose,You are planning international travel. Share your nationality destination and trip purpose.,Check visa requirements,Hello! What is your nationality and which country are you visiting?,Visa policies change frequently. Always verify with the destination embassy.,easy,"travel, visa, immigration",Visa Guide,
travel-car-rental_chatbot,travel,Compare car rental options by vehicle class rental duration and insurance needs,You need a rental car. Share your destination dates and vehicle preferences.,Find a rental car,Hello! Where and when do you need a rental car?,I need your pickup location and dates to search for cars.,easy,"travel, car-rental, transportation",Car Rental Guide,
travel-vacation-package_chatbot,travel,Find and compare vacation packages bundling flight hotel and activities,"You and your partner want a 7-day all-inclusive beach vacation in Cancun for under $3,000 total, including flights and hotel.",Find a vacation package,Hello! Where are you thinking of going for vacation?,I need your destination and approximate dates to find packages.,medium,"travel, packages, vacation",Vacation Planner,
travel-cruise-booking_chatbot,travel,Compare cruise itineraries cabin types and onboard amenities,You are considering a cruise. Share your preferred region duration and budget.,Compare cruise options,Hello! What region are you interested in cruising to?,Cruise itineraries and pricing vary by season. I can give general guidance.,medium,"travel, cruise, maritime",Cruise Advisor,
travel-insurance_chatbot,travel,Compare travel insurance plans covering medical cancellation and baggage,"You're spending $2,500 on a non-refundable trip to Japan next month and are worried about medical coverage abroad.",Compare travel insurance plans,Hello! Where are you traveling and what coverage are you most concerned about?,Travel insurance policies vary. Read the fine print on pre-existing conditions and exclusions.,easy,"travel, insurance, protection",Travel Insurance Guide,
travel-airport-lounges_chatbot,travel,Find airport lounge access options including membership programs and day passes,You have a layover or want lounge access. Share your airport and travel class.,Find lounge access options,Hello! Which airport are you flying through?,Lounge access depends on your airline ticket class and membership programs.,easy,"travel, airport, lounges",Lounge Finder,
travel-baggage-policy_chatbot,travel,Understand airline baggage policies including allowances fees and lost bag procedures,You need to know baggage rules for your flight. Share your airline and fare type.,Check baggage policies,Hello! Which airline are you flying with and what is your fare type?,Baggage policies vary by airline and fare class. Check your ticket for exact allowances.,easy,"travel, baggage, luggage",Baggage Guide,
travel-delay-compensation_chatbot,travel,Understand your rights and compensation options when a flight is delayed or canceled,Your flight was delayed or canceled. Share the airline and delay details.,Check compensation eligibility,Hello! I can help with delay compensation. Which airline and how long was the delay?,Compensation rules depend on the airline's policy and the jurisdiction of the flight.,easy,"travel, delays, compensation",Travel Rights Guide,
legal-small-claims_chatbot,legal,Understand the small claims court process and whether your case qualifies,You have a dispute and are considering small claims court. Describe the situation.,Understand small claims options,Hello! I provide legal information not advice. What is your dispute about?,Consult a legal aid clinic or attorney for your specific situation.,easy,"legal, small-claims, dispute",Legal Information Assistant,
legal-employment-rights_chatbot,legal,Learn about workplace rights regarding discrimination harassment wages and leave,You have a workplace concern. Describe what happened.,Understand your employment rights,Hello! What workplace situation are you dealing with?,Consider speaking with an employment attorney for personalized guidance.,medium,"legal, employment, workers-rights",Employment Rights Guide,
legal-immigration-basics_chatbot,legal,Get an overview of immigration paths including visa types green cards and citizenship,You are exploring immigration options. Share your current status and goals.,Understand immigration pathways,Hello! What is your current immigration status and what is your goal?,Consult a licensed immigration attorney for personalized advice.,medium,"legal, immigration, visa",Immigration Guide,
legal-consumer-protection_chatbot,legal,Understand your rights as a consumer regarding false advertising defective products and unfair practices,You believe a business treated you unfairly. Describe what happened.,Understand consumer protection rights,Hello! I can explain consumer protection rights. What happened with the purchase or service?,Consumer protection laws vary by state. Consider filing a complaint with your state attorney general.,easy,"legal, consumer, rights",Consumer Rights Guide,
legal-bankruptcy-basics_chatbot,legal,Understand bankruptcy types chapter 7 vs 13 and whether it might be right for your situation,You are struggling with debt and considering bankruptcy. Share your financial situation.,Understand bankruptcy options,Hello! I can explain bankruptcy basics. This is legal information not advice. What kind of debt are you dealing with?,Bankruptcy has serious long-term consequences. Consult a bankruptcy attorney before deciding.,hard,"legal, bankruptcy, debt",Bankruptcy Information,
legal-ip-basics_chatbot,legal,Learn about intellectual property types including copyright trademark and patent basics,You have a creative work or invention and want to protect it. Share what you created.,Understand intellectual property options,Hello! I can explain IP protection types. What did you create or invent?,IP law is complex. Consider consulting an IP attorney for your specific situation.,easy,"legal, intellectual-property, copyright",IP Guide,
legal-business-formation_chatbot,legal,Understand business structure options including LLC corporation and sole proprietorship,You and two friends want to start a mobile app development company. You're unsure whether to form an LLC or a corporation.,Choose a business structure,Hello! What type of business are you starting and how many founders?,Business formation has legal and tax implications. Consult an attorney and accountant.,medium,"legal, business, startup",Business Formation Guide,
legal-child-custody_chatbot,legal,Understand child custody types and factors courts consider in custody decisions,You are going through a separation involving children. The chatbot explains custody types and considerations.,Understand child custody basics,Hello! I can explain child custody types. This is legal information not advice. What is your situation?,Child custody is highly fact-specific. You need a family law attorney for your case.,hard,"legal, family, custody",Family Law Guide,
legal-traffic-tickets_chatbot,legal,Understand options for handling a traffic ticket including payment defensive driving and contesting,You received a traffic ticket. Share the violation type and your state.,Understand traffic ticket options,Hello! I can explain traffic ticket options. What was the violation and in which state?,Traffic laws vary by jurisdiction. Consider consulting a traffic attorney for serious violations.,easy,"legal, traffic, tickets",Traffic Ticket Guide,
legal-estate-planning_chatbot,legal,Understand estate planning tools including wills trusts power of attorney and healthcare directives,"You own a home worth $400,000 and have two young children. You want to ensure they are cared for if something happens to you.",Understand estate planning options,Hello! Estate planning helps protect your wishes. Do you have a will already?,Estate planning is highly personal. Consult an estate planning attorney for documents tailored to your situation.,medium,"legal, estate-planning, will",Estate Planning Guide,
