real-estate-property-tax-appeal_chatbot,real-estate,Learn how to appeal your property tax assessment and prepare supporting evidence,Your property tax assessment seems too high. The chatbot explains the appeal process.,Understand how to appeal property taxes,Hello! When did you receive your assessment and what seems inaccurate?,I need more details about your situation. When was your assessment issued?,easy,"real-estate, property-tax, appeal",Tax Appeal Guide,
real-estate-selling-home_chatbot,real-estate,Get guidance on selling your home including pricing staging offers and closing,You need to sell your 3-bedroom house in the suburbs within 3 months because you've accepted a job in another state.,Navigate the home selling process,Hello! I can help with selling your home. What is your timeline for selling?,Work with a local real estate agent for accurate pricing and market advice.,medium,"real-estate, selling, home",Home Selling Guide,
real-estate-refinancing_chatbot,real-estate,Understand mortgage refinancing options including rate-and-term and cash-out refinancing,You are considering refinancing your mortgage. Share your current rate and goal.,Explore refinancing options,Hello! What is your current mortgage rate and what are you hoping to achieve?,Refinancing may not make sense for everyone. Consider closing costs and how long you plan to stay.,medium,"real-estate, mortgage, refinance",Refinance Guide,
