real-estate-home-renovation_chatbot,real-estate,Get guidance on home renovation projects including budgeting contractor selection and permits,"You want to remodel your outdated kitchen with a budget of $25,000 and need advice on hiring contractors and getting permits.",Plan your home renovation,Hello! What room or area are you planning to renovate?,Renovation costs vary significantly by location and material choices. Get multiple contractor quotes.,medium,"real-estate, renovation, remodeling",Renovation Advisor,
