gardening-composting-guide_chatbot,gardening,Get started with composting for your garden including bin selection materials and troubleshooting,"You have a small urban yard and want to start composting kitchen scraps to improve your sandy soil, but you're worried about smell and pests.",Start composting at home,Hello! I can help with composting. What is your outdoor setup and how much waste do you generate?,A healthy compost pile needs a balance of greens nitrogen and browns carbon materials.,easy,"gardening, compost, soil",Composting Guide,
music-instrument-beginner_chatbot,music,Get started learning a musical instrument including instrument selection and practice routines,"You've always wanted to play the acoustic guitar and just bought a used Yamaha F310, but you've never played any instrument before.",Start learning an instrument,Hello! I can help with getting started. Which instrument are you drawn to?,Learning an instrument takes time. Consistent short practice sessions are more effective than occasional marathon sessions.,easy,"music, learning, instruments",Music Teacher,
